<p>Patterns that are not yet enabled by default remain configurable in your push protection settings.</p>
<h2 id="validity-checks-added" id="validity-checks-added" ><a class="heading-link" href="#validity-checks-added">Validity checks added<span class="heading-hash pl-2 text-italic text-bold" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></h2>
